    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>chopped shallot</strong>,<strong> garlic</strong> and<strong> coriander</strong> in a bowl with the <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!),<strong> red wine vinegar</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>chimichurri</strong></p>",
